steps.html_instructions: Head west on E Pearl St toward S Lamar St
Slight left toward University Blvd
At the traffic circle, take the 2nd exit onto University Blvd
Continue onto Terry Rd
Turn right to merge onto I-20 W toward Vicksburg

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-20 W, follow signs for Vicksburg
Passing through Louisiana
Entering Texas
Keep right at the fork to continue on TX-557 Spur W, follow signs for US-80 W/Dallas
Continue onto US-80 W
Continue onto I-30 W
Keep right to stay on I-30 W
Take exit 44A to merge onto I-35E N toward Denton
Keep left at the fork to continue on TX-183 W, follow signs for Texas 183/Texas 114/Irving/DFW Airport
Keep right at the fork to continue on Hwy 114 W/TX-114 W, follow signs for Grapevine/Airport North Entry
Keep left to continue on Hwy 114 W
Keep right at the fork to continue on Hwy 114 W/Rte 114 W/State 114 W/State Rte 114 W/TX-114 W
Slight right onto Rte 114 W/State 114 W/State Rte 114 W/TX-114 W

Merge onto TX-114 W/U.S. 287 N/US-81 N via the ramp on the left to Decatur/Bridgeport
Continue to follow U.S. 287 N
Keep right at the fork to stay on U.S. 287 N
Continue onto I-44 E/U.S. 287 N
Take exit 3A on the left toward US-287 N/Vernon/Amarillo
Continue onto U.S. 287 N

Take the ramp on the left onto I-40 W/U.S. 287 N
Continue to follow I-40 W
Entering New Mexico
Take exit 159B-159C for I-25 S/I-25 N toward Las Cruces/Santa Fe
Keep right at the fork to continue on Exit 159C, follow signs for I-25 N/Santa Fe and merge onto I-25 N
Take exit 242 for NM-165 E toward US-550 W/Bernalillo/Placitas

Turn left onto NM-165 W/US-550 N (signs for Sandoval County Station)
Continue to follow US-550 N
Turn left onto Co Rd 7010
Turn right onto Co Rd 7100
Turn right onto NM-371 N
Turn left onto US-64 BYP W/W Murray Dr

US-64 BYP W/W Murray Dr turns left and becomes US-64 W/W Main St
Continue to follow US-64 W

Turn right onto US-491 N
Entering Colorado

Slight left onto US-491 N/S Broadway (signs for I-491)
Continue to follow US-491 N
Entering Utah

Turn right onto US-191 N/N Main St
Continue to follow US-191 N
Turn left to merge onto I-70 W
Take exit 157 to merge onto US-191 N/US-6 W toward Price/Salt Lake
Keep left to continue on US-6 W
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-15 N/Salt Lake City and merge onto I-15 N
Take exit 306 for 600 S
Continue onto W 600 S
Turn left onto S Main St
